                                        Welcome to Shanta Life Insurance! We’ll be here to protect what matters the most to you. Be ready to explore our insurance solutions for peace of mind and financial security.
                                    </p>
                                    <ul class="footer-socialicons">
                                        <li><a href="https://www.facebook.com/people/Shanta-Life-Insurance/61566152682701/?_rdr"><i class="zmdi zmdi-facebook"></i></a></li>
                                        <li><a href="@Html.Raw("https://youtube.com/@shantalifeinsurance?si=FZ7je5u8sVL8n86K")"><i class="zmdi zmdi-youtube"></i></a></li>
